    <fr:p>Let <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[G]]></fr:tex>, <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[G']]></fr:tex>, and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[G'']]></fr:tex> be the groups defined by <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[V]]></fr:tex>, <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[V']]></fr:tex>, and <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[V'']]></fr:tex>, respectively.
