      then a power of <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\chi ]]></fr:tex> factors through <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[{G''}^0]]></fr:tex>, and so <fr:tex display="inline"><![CDATA[\chi ]]></fr:tex> is trivial.</fr:p>
